"text/plain","offset":0,"remaining_read_bytes_for_opportunity":520561,"remaining_reads_for_opportunity":31,"sha256":"ddd2d95cd7358535623acb85629f87f4c9bf2a81d0c2fa72ac90da32a9d81789","total_size_bytes":3727},"turn":{"attempts_max":3,"attempts_remaining":3,"completed":false,"deadline":"2026-06-29T21:53:53.106044978Z","deliberation_round":3,"member_id":"C1","opportunity_id":"deliberation:3:C1","phase":"deliberation","remaining_ms":890024,"role_id":"council","turn_number":17}},"isError":false},"server":"aar","tool":"read_evidence_range"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782769143082},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me decode the base64 content to read the transcript:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1066","name":"bash","arguments":{"command":"echo \"\" | base64 -d"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":3622,"output":3277,"cacheRead":36096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42995,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782769143083,"responseId":"gen-1782769143-RHo0WUFghycIM1d2cZGo"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1066","toolName":"bash","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Source: GovInfo PDF DCPD-202501162, \"Remarks in an Exchange With Reporters Prior to the 2026 Federation Internationale des Associations de Football (FIFA) World Cup Draw\".\nDate shown in PDF: December 5, 2025.\nPDF opening text: \"Administration of Donald J. Trump, 2025\" and title \"Remarks in an Exchange With Reporters Prior to the 2026 Federation Internationale des Associations de Football (FIFA) World Cup Draw\". The transcript begins: \"[The President's remarks were joined in progress.]\"\n\nMaterial transcript extract from the GovInfo-rendered PDF:\n\n2026 World Cup Draw Event/John F. Kennedy Center for the Performing Arts\nQ. Mr. President, what do you think about the crowd?\nThe President. Oh, look, the new star--[inaudible].\nCongratulations.\nQ. Thank you.\nThe President. You're the new star of television and Fox.\nQ. Thank you. How are you doing, Mr. President?\nThe President. I'm doing very well.\nQ. What do you think about the crowd here?\nThe President. I think the crowd is great, and I think the building is great. We've made a lot of improvements over the last 6 months. Taking--the Kennedy Center was in very bad shape. Now it's getting to be really good. And in 6 months, it's going to be incredible with the improvements we've made.\nQ. The first time for the U.S. to host since the nineties.\nThe President. Right.\nQ. Are you ready for it?\nThe President. I'm ready for it, and they're ready for it. And Gianni, who you know--\nMr. Infantino. Yes.\nThe President. --has done a fantastic job with FIFA. And we're looking to have--you know, we're set--we have already set records for tickets sales. I don't think there's ever been anything like it in any sport. And so, I want to congratulate yo�K��\\��\u0012[��[�\u001a[�ˈ\u0015\u001a\u0018[��\u001e[�K��\u001a\u0019H\u0014\u001c�\\�Y\u0019[�\u000b�\u0012H\u0019\u001bۉ�\b\u0019]�[�\u001a\u0018]�H\u001d\u001b�\u001d�Z]\u000b�\u0010�]\b\u001bXZ�܈\u001c�X�ܙ\u001c�\u001a\u0018]�H\u0018�Y[�\u001c�]\u000b����\f��\u0015�ܛ\u0019\b\u0010�\\\b\u0011\u001c�]�\u0011]�[�\u0002�K�\u0014��\u0018�[�\u001e[�H\u001d\u0019[\u001b\b\u001bYH\u0018X��]\b\u001d\u001a\u001a\\�\u0018�Y�\u0019\u0018^H\u001d\u001b�\u0018^Oʕ\u001a\u0019H\u0014\u001c�\\�Y\u0019[�\u000b�\u0012]\t��\u001a�\\�\b\u0018H\u0018�Y�\u0019\u0018^K\b\u0018[�\b\u001a]\t��\u0018H\u0019ܙX]\b\u001c�\u001bܝ\u000b�\u0010[�\b\u001a]\b\u001c�X[\u001b\u001eH\u001a\\�\u0018��Z[��\u001d\u001b�\u0010[Y\\�X�K�\u0010[�\b\u001b�]�\\�K[�؛�\u001eH\u0019]�\\�\u001d\u001a\u001b�Y�\u001d\b\u0018H\u001d\u001a\u001a[��\u001b\u001aZ�H\u001d\u001a\u001a\\�\u0018��[\u0019\b\u001a\u0018\\\u001c\u0019[��\u0010[�\b\u0012I�H\u001d�\\�H\u001a\u0018\\\u001c\u001eH\u001d\u001b�\u001c�^H\u001d\u001a\u0018]\b\u001d�IݙH\u0018[\u001c�XY\