chedule to assign a date, time and location to each match on Saturday, Dec. 6.\"\n\nUnder heading HOW TO WATCH IN ENGLISH & SPANISH:\n\"The final draw will be broadcast live on FOX with English commentary; pre-draw coverage begins at 11:30 a.m. ET, the draw will take place between 12 and 2 p.m. ET, and post-draw analysis will conclude at 3 p.m. ET.\"\n\n\"The final draw will also be available to stream on FIFA.com. Spanish radio coverage of the final draw will be available on Futbol de Primera.\"\n\nCapture limitations: the page HTML is large and script-heavy, but these paragraphs were present in the retrieved HTML/Next.js data. This extract is submitted only for the scheduled time and broadcast-window facts, not for the Ronaldo utterance."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782769306221},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have all the key evidence. Let me examine the market page and terms to understand the exact wording:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dbfc","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_stat_evidence","args":"{\"evidence_id\":\"ev_2c7c2c8a2d76_market-page\"}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":413,"output":65,"cacheRead":53184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53662,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782769306223,"responseId":"gen-1782769306-xxZoK9yFx8zEyTiDSqwr"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dbfc","toolName":"mcp","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C1\ncase_id: arb-ex03a-20260629210937\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:3:C1\nremaining_ms: 725116\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex03a-20260629210937\",\"member_id\":\"C1\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"evidence\":{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:09:45Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_2c7c2c8a2d76_market-page\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\"